result.name: 聚好味

reviews.text:
The food is very delicious, should try when you come and visit HK, although a little bit difficult in order because language barrier, but still we manage to order a very high quality delicious local foods. 

We order one steam fish, egg with shrimp, fried garlic tofu, stir-fry choisam(green vegetable), and yang chow fried rice.

Must try!!
D嘢好食，牛腩，黃金笳子， 海蜇手撕雞👍
下午茶抵食,牛腩一流。我食幾次都係比半肥瘦牛腩我,真係好好食,入口即容。下次要試下晚上小菜。
服務一流，食物多選擇，無得頂
超抵下午茶
